      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Event Replay mode — Timeline Controller\n\nThis dashboard demonstrates Event Replay: the Timeline Controller panel below has a **panel-saved time range** configured in its options, independent of the dashboard's time picker. It writes `timeFrom` / `timeTo` / `step` template variables on every tick across that saved range. The Stat panels query Prometheus at the current window with PromQL's `@` modifier; the rate panel uses `$step` in its `[range]` bracket.\n\nPress **Play forward** to start. Change the dashboard's time picker — the replay window stays anchored to its configured range.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.0",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "event",
        "event": {
          "horizontalAlignment": "center",
          "initialPosition": "start",
          "showProgressTrack": true,
          "tickIntervalMs": 1000,
          "timeStep": "5m",
          "variableFrom": "timeFrom",
          "variableTo": "timeTo",
          "variableStep": "step",
          "boundaryFrom": 1779408000000,
          "boundaryTo": 1779451200000,
          "verticalAlignment": "middle"
        }
      },
      "pluginVersion": "1.0.0",
      "title": "",
      "type": "evaldasguogis-timelinecontroller-panel"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-demo"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 60 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 80 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prom-demo"
          },
          "expr": "100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[$step] @ ${timeTo:date:seconds})) * 100)",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "CPU at playhead",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "CPU at playhead (%)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
